    "Proof: By hypothesis Σ C \\ Σ C ′ has two connected boundary components S and Ŝ′ corresponding to those of Σ C and Σ C ′ as stated.",
    "Let C ′′ be the region consisting of all faces, edges, and vertices contained in the annulus Σ and a ∈ Tube S ′ corresponding to a string diagram y on S ′ × I.",
